OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTaliban arrest Afghan      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgirls' education activist  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A prominent Afghan campaigner for      
OL,6, female education has been arrested by  
OL,7, the Taliban, even as teenage girls and 
OL,8, women remain barred from classrooms.   
OL,10,FMatiullah Wesa, 30, had often received 
OL,11,Fthreats - he has spent years travelling
OL,12,Facross Afghanistan trying to improve   
OL,13,Faccess to education for all children.  
OL,15,FThe Taliban did not say why Mr Wesa is 
OL,16,Fin custody. His house was also raided. 
OL,18,FHis arrest follows the detention of a  
OL,19,Fnumber of other activists who have been
OL,20,Fcampaigning for women's education.     
